      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published rotating-machinery validation studies. Sensitivity analysis comparing k-epsilon and SST k-omega shows < 7% difference in RH at all operating points. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model is the accepted standard for CFD hemolysis prediction in this shear range."
    },
