    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed and meet or exceed their required gradation levels at MRL 3. The Equivalency of input parameters factor was not formally assessed on the grounds that simulation and experimental inputs were specified to be identical; the assessment team judged this a non-issue. The overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision that CFD-predicted hemolysis identifies worst-case operating conditions for the CPB device.",
